name: Peace Cymbal earrings
description:
Wear a peace symbol that is truly a piece of a cymbal! These earrings from our Cymbalism collection are the perfect accompaniment for the Peace Cymbal pendant. The interior shapes of the peace charms are individually cut by hand from a reclaimed drum cymbal with a jeweler's saw, suspended within a recycled guitar string, joined with brass wire, and completed with a handmade gold-fill ear wire.

Charm diameter: .75”
Total length: 1.25”

NOTE: Your piece is made to order, and will ship in 5-7 business days.
